 description Text, and FieldError. Renders the shared frame (label, border, description, error) around field content and manages accessibility."},"82":{"id":"/docs/components/field-frame-13","page_id":"/docs/components/field-frame","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/field-frame#features","content":"**Visual frame**: Shared border, focus, disabled, and invalid styling around field content"},"83":{"id":"/docs/components/field-frame-14","page_id":"/docs/components/field-frame","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/field-frame#features","content":"**Focus delegation**: Tracks focus from any focusable child (input, button) via `data-focus-within` and `data-focus-visible`"},"84":{"id":"/docs/components/field-frame-15","page_id":"/docs/components/field-frame","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/field-frame#features","content":"**Label, description, error**: Optional Label, helper Text, and FieldError with proper accessibility association"},"85":{"id":"/docs/components/field-frame-16","page_id":"/docs/components/field-frame","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/field-frame#features","content":"**Required indicator**: Shows asterisk next to label when the field is required"},"86":{"id":"/docs/components/field-frame-17","page_id":"/docs/components/field-frame","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/field-frame#features","content":"**React Aria integration**: Uses Provider pattern so nested elements stay in sync with the frame"},"87":{"id":"/docs/components/field-frame-18","page_id":"/docs/components/field-frame","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/field-frame#features","content":"**Field wrapper composition**: Designed to sit inside TextField, NumberField, DateField, or Select as the main field UI"},"88":{"id":"/docs/components/field-frame-19","page_id":"/docs/components/field-frame","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/field-frame#props","content":"FieldFrame accepts the following props:"},"89":{"i