id":"/docs/components/icon","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/icon#icon-not-loading","content":"Icon Not Loading"},"148":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-37","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/icon#performance-issues","content":"Performance Issues"},"149":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-38","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon","content":"The `Icon` component provides a flexible and performant way to display SVG icons with extensive customization options. Built on top of the Bento Icon system, it features on-demand loading from a CDN, automatic caching, and enhanced props for the Antares design system."},"150":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-39","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**On-demand loading**: Icons are loaded asynchronously from CDN only when needed"},"151":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-40","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Automatic caching**: Once loaded, icons are cached for optimal performance"},"152":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-41","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Flexible sizing**: Support for `width` and `height` props"},"153":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-42","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Color inheritance**: Uses `currentColor` by default for seamless theme integration"},"154":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-43","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Accessibility ready**: Built-in support for screen readers and keyboard navigation"},"155":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-44","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**TypeScript support**: Fully typed with comprehensive prop interfaces"},"156":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-45","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Bento integration**: Extends Bento Icon with additional Antares-specific features"},"157":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-46","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#props","content":"The `Icon` component accepts the following props:"},"158":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-47","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"The component extends `BentoIconProps` and passes through all standard HTML attributes and accessibility props to the underlying Bento Icon component. This includes:"},"159":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-48","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Accessibility**: `aria-label`, `aria-describedby`, `role`, `title`"},"160":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-49","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Events**: `onClick`, `onMouseOver`, `onFocus`, etc."},"161":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-50","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Styling**: `className`, `style`, `data-*` attributes"},"162":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-51","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Transform**: `rotate`, `flip` for icon transformations"},"163":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-52","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#size-variants","content":"Specify explicit width and height values:"},"164":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-53","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comp